title: Registration
content:
Registration is now closed, if you haven't completed steps 2 through 4 yet, please do so as soon as possible:

Step 2: Complete Trek Contract (youth only): Trek Contract

Step 3: Complete Medical Consent Form (youth and adults): Medical Consent Form

Step 4: If your Medical Consent form lists any medical conditions, you must print the Medical Release Form, obtain your doctor's signature, and email the form to bountifulheightsstake@gmail.com (youth and adults): Medical Release Form
